{"title":"How to change your Apple Watch ringtone and alert sounds","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2463582/how-to-change-your-apple-watch-ringtone-and-alert-sounds.html","date":1729509300000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s almost crazy to think it, but for the last decade Apple has not allowed you to change the default ringtone, notification sounds, or alerts on your Apple Watch. Finally, watchOS 11 gives us this very basic capability, but you’d be forgiven for not knowing about it because it’s not in the <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-us/121163\">watchOS 11 release notes</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s how you change the default ringtone and other sounds on your Apple Watch with watchOS 11.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Change ringtones and sounds using your Apple Watch</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>On your Apple Watch, open Settings then scroll down and tap <em>Sound &amp; Haptics</em>. (Press the Digital Crown to see your full list of applications.) In the <em>Sound &amp; Haptics</em> settings, you have to scroll a screen or two down to find the settings for various sounds. You can change these six alert sounds:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Ringtone</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Text Tone</li>\n\n\n\n<li>New Mail</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Calendar Alerts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reminder Alerts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Default Alerts</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Apple Watch ringtones\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2618w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Apple Watch ringtones\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2618w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Apple Watch ringtones\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2618w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-how-to.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Change ringtone and sounds using your iPhone</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Like most Apple Watch settings, it’s easier to change these settings using a linked iPhone. Open the Watch app, then select <em>Sound &amp; Haptics</em>. You’ll find the same six sound settings there.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-app-how-to.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Apple Watch ringtones app\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-app-how-to.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 4741w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/watch-ringtones-app-how-to.jpg?resize=300%2C206&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-content